            "body": "Currently, rules.bzl produces an error on renaming that looks like:\r\n\r\n```\r\nFileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: 'truffle/utils_native.so' -> 'bazel-out/darwin-fastbuild/genfiles/truffle/utils_native.so'\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis is because the rename script doesn't account for the extension being there. It expects the extension to be a raw `.so` instead of `.cpython-36m-darwin.so`",
