            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I fixed this in my repo using glob and updating the rule command as such:\r\n```\r\n        cmd = \"PYTHONHASHSEED=0 $(location @cython//:cythonize) -k -i %s $(SRCS)\" % extra_flags +\r\n              # Rename outputs to expected location.\r\n              \"\"\" && python3 -c 'import os, sys, glob; n = len(sys.argv); [os.rename(glob.glob(src.split(\".\")[0] + \".*.so\")[0], dst) for src, dst in zip(sys.argv[1:], sys.argv[1+n//2:])]' $(SRCS) $(OUTS)\"\"\",\r\n```",
